  "keyFeatures": [
    "Long-horizon deterministic benchmark testing agent coherence over hundreds of turns",
    "SQLite-backed discrete-event simulation of AI startup operations",
    "Multi-domain prestige system with decay mechanics",
    "Employee productivity inference through hidden skill rates",
    "Compounding decisions with deadline pressure and cash flow management",
    "Five difficulty presets from tutorial to nightmare mode"
